<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col col-md col-6 col-md-offset-3 col-sm-12">
      <div class="mt50"></div>
      <h1>Pay your pledge on line</h1>
     
     <%= render 'form' %>
     </div>
   </div>     
   <div class="row">    
     <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
       <div class="pledge-text">
        <p><strong> You have elected the <span id="plan"><em><%= @pledge.plan %></em></span> pay plan for your annual pledge of <%= number_to_currency(@pledge.amount) %>. That would be <%= @pledge.divisor %> payments of <span id="payThis"><%= number_to_currency((@pledge.pay_this.to_f)/100) %></span>.</strong></p>
        <div class="mt30"></div>
          <p>If these numbers are not correct, click "edit pledge" to make changes. If OK, click "Pay with Card." You will be taken to a secure website that handles credit and debit card payments for our church.</p>
        <div class="mt30"></div>
        <p><strong>
          If your circumstances change or for any other reason you wish to edit or remove these settings you may do so at any time.</strong></p>
     </div>
  </div>  
</div>
